2. Meaningful Names

It should tell you why it exists, what is does, and how it used.
> intention-revealing function, explicit

1.What kinds of things are in the function?
2. What is the significance of the zeroth subscript of an item in the function?
3. What is the significance of the value 4?
4. How would I use the list being returned? 

